::Ender::
       He took both the punch and the kick to the head but somehow managed to 
avoid getting shot for once, until they ricocheted off of a rock and hit him 
in the back ... again.  He sighed bringing his head back to it's normal 
position.  "You see it's too many blows to the head like that that make me 
the way I am."  He shakes his head disparagingly.  He reaches behind him and 
comes back with a sword in his hand.  "Now what the hell was that doing 
there.  Ah well."  He places it in it's sheath.  He then aims a very quick 
punch toward Rodimus Prime's head.

--part1_41.1f96563f.2a553134_boundary
